vernac_cmds: Require Import Setoid Morphisms RelationClasses Program.Basics Omega.
Class Inhabited (A : Type) := { cinhabited : inhabited A}.

Class ILogicOps (A : Type) : Type := { lentails: A -> A -> Prop; ltrue: A; lfalse: A; limpl: A -> A -> A; land: A -> A -> A; lor: A -> A -> A; lforall: forall {T : Type}, (T -> A) -> A; lexists: forall {T : Type}, (T -> A) -> A }.
Notation "'Forall' x : T , p" := (lforall (fun x : T => p)) (at level 78, x ident, right associativity).
Notation "'Forall' x , p" := (lforall (fun x => p)) (at level 78, x ident, right associativity, only parsing).
Notation "'Exists' x : T , p" := (lexists (fun x : T => p)) (at level 78, x ident, right associativity).
Notation "'Exists' x , p" := (lexists (fun x => p)) (at level 78, x ident, right associativity, only parsing).
Definition lequiv P Q := P |-- Q /\ Q |-- P.

Class ILogic {A : Type} {ILOps: ILogicOps A} : Type := { lentailsPre:> PreOrder lentails; ltrueR: forall (C : A), C |-- ltrue; lfalseL: forall (C : A), lfalse |-- C; lforallL: forall (T : Type) x (P: T -> A) C, P x |-- C -> lforall P |-- C; lforallR: forall (T : Type) (P: T -> A) C, (forall x, C |-- P x) -> C |-- lforall P; lexistsL: forall (T : Type) (P: T -> A) C, (forall x, P x |-- C) -> lexists P |-- C; lexistsR: forall (T : Type) (x : T) (P: T -> A) C, C |-- P x -> C |-- lexists P; landL1: forall (P Q C : A), P |-- C -> P //\\ Q |-- C; landL2: forall (P Q C : A), Q |-- C -> P //\\ Q |-- C; lorR1: forall (P Q C : A), C |-- P -> C |-- P \\// Q; lorR2: forall (P Q C : A), C |-- Q -> C |-- P \\// Q; landR: forall (P Q C : A), C |-- P -> C |-- Q -> C |-- P //\\ Q; lorL: forall (P Q C : A), P |-- C -> Q |-- C -> P \\// Q |-- C; landAdj: forall (P Q C : A), C |-- (P -->> Q) -> C //\\ P |-- Q; limplAdj: forall (P Q C : A), C //\\ P |-- Q -> C |-- (P -->> Q) }.
Arguments lforallL {A ILOps ILogic} [T] x P C _.
Arguments lexistsR {A ILOps ILogic} [T] x P C _.
Notation "|-- P" := (ltrue |-- P) (at level 85, no associativity).
Hint Extern 0 (?P |-- ?Q) => (is_evar P; reflexivity) || (is_evar Q; reflexivity).
intros P Q R [HPQ HQP] [HQR HRQ]; split; etransitivity; eassumption.
Lemma land_is_forall P Q : P //\\ Q -|- Forall b : bool, if b then P else Q.
apply lforallR; intro x; destruct x.
Lemma lor_is_exists P Q: P \\// Q -|- Exists b : bool, if b then P else Q.
apply lexistsL; intro x; destruct x.
Lemma ltrue_is_forall: ltrue -|- Forall x: Empty_set, Empty_set_rect _ x.
Lemma lfalse_is_exists: lfalse -|- Exists x: Empty_set, Empty_set_rect _ x.
Global Instance lequiv_lentails : subrelation lequiv lentails.
Global Instance lequiv_flip_lentails: subrelation lequiv (flip lentails).
Global Instance lforall_lentails_m: Proper (pointwise_relation T lentails ++> lentails) lforall.
apply lforallR; intro x; apply lforallL with x.
Global Instance lforall_lequiv_m: Proper (pointwise_relation T lequiv ++> lequiv) lforall.
intros P P' HP; split; apply lforall_lentails_m; intro x; apply HP.
Global Instance lexists_lentails_m: Proper (pointwise_relation T lentails ++> lentails) lexists.
apply lexistsL; intro x; apply lexistsR with x.
Global Instance lexists_lequiv_m: Proper (pointwise_relation T lequiv ++> lequiv) lexists.
intros P P' HP; split; apply lexists_lentails_m; intro x; apply HP.
Global Instance : Proper (lequiv ==> lequiv ==> iff) lequiv.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ; split; intros H.
Global Instance lequiv_lentails_m : Proper (lequiv ==> lequiv ==> iff) lentails.
Global Instance lentails_lentails_m: Proper (lentails --> lentails ++> impl) lentails.
Global Instance land_lentails_m: Proper (lentails ++> lentails ++> lentails) land.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ.
apply landR; [apply landL1 | apply landL2]; assumption.
Global Instance land_lequiv_m: Proper (lequiv ==> lequiv ==> lequiv) land.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ.
split; apply land_lentails_m; (apply HP || apply HQ).
Global Instance lor_lentails_m: Proper (lentails ++> lentails ++> lentails) lor.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ.
apply lorL; [apply lorR1 | apply lorR2]; assumption.
Global Instance lor_lequiv_m: Proper (lequiv ==> lequiv ==> lequiv) lor.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ.
split; apply lor_lentails_m; (apply HP || apply HQ).
Global Instance limpl_lentails_m: Proper (lentails --> lentails ++> lentails) limpl.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ; red in HP.
apply limplAdj; rewrite <- HQ, HP; apply landAdj; reflexivity.
Global Instance limpl_lequiv_m: Proper (lequiv ==> lequiv ==> lequiv) limpl.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ.
split; apply limpl_lentails_m; (apply HP || apply HQ).
Hint Extern 0 (?P -|- ?Q) => (is_evar P; reflexivity) || (is_evar Q; reflexivity).
Lemma lforwardL {A} `{IL: ILogic A} {Q R}: Q |-- R -> forall P G, P |-- Q -> (P |-- R -> G) -> G.
intros HQR P G HPQ HG.
Tactic Notation "lforwardL" hyp(H) := eapply (lforwardL H); clear H; [|intros H].
Ltac landR := repeat match goal with | |- _ |-- _ //\\ _ => apply landR end.
Ltac landL := repeat match goal with | |- ?L1 //\\ ?L2 |-- ?R => match L1 with | context [R] => apply landL1 | _ => match L2 with | context [R] => apply landL2 end end end.
Lemma landC P Q: P //\\ Q -|- Q //\\ P.
Lemma landA P Q R: (P //\\ Q) //\\ R -|- P //\\ (Q //\\ R).
Lemma lorC P Q : P \\// Q -|- Q \\// P.
split; apply lorL; [apply lorR2 | apply lorR1 | apply lorR2 | apply lorR1]; reflexivity.
Lemma lorA P Q R : (P \\// Q) \\// R -|- P \\// (Q \\// R).
split; apply lorL; try apply lorL; [ apply lorR1 | apply lorR2; apply lorR1 | apply lorR2; apply lorR2 | apply lorR1; apply lorR1 | apply lorR1; apply lorR2 | apply lorR2 ]; reflexivity.
Lemma limplValid P Q: |-- P -->> Q <-> P |-- Q.
Lemma limplL P Q CL CR (HP: CL |-- P) (HR: Q //\\ CL |-- CR) : (P -->> Q) //\\ CL |-- CR.
apply landR; [apply landAdj | apply landL2]; reflexivity.
Lemma limplAdj2 P Q R : P -->> Q -->> R -|- P //\\ Q -->> R.
Lemma landexistsDL1 (f : T -> A) (P : A) : lexists f //\\ P |-- Exists a, (f a //\\ P).
apply landAdj; apply lexistsL; intro a; apply limplAdj; apply lexistsR with a; reflexivity.
Lemma landexistsDL2 (f : T -> A) (P : A) : P //\\ lexists f |-- Exists a, (P //\\ f a).
Lemma landexistsDR1 (f : T -> A) (P : A) : Exists a, (f a //\\ P) |-- lexists f //\\ P.
apply lexistsL; intro a; apply landR.
apply landL1; apply lexistsR with a; reflexivity.
Lemma landexistsDR2 (f : T -> A) (P : A) : Exists a, (P //\\ f a) |-- P //\\ lexists f.
Lemma landexistsD1 (f : T -> A) (P : A) : (Exists a, f a) //\\ P -|- Exists a, (f a //\\ P).
Lemma lorexistsDL (f : T -> A) (P : A) {H : Inhabited T} : (Exists a, f a) \\// P |-- Exists a, (f a \\// P).
apply lexistsL; intro x; apply lexistsR with x; apply lorR1; reflexivity.
destruct H as [[x]]; apply lexistsR with x; apply lorR2; reflexivity.
Lemma lorexistsDR (f : T -> A) (P : A) : Exists a, (f a \\// P) |-- (Exists a, f a) \\// P.
apply lexistsL; intro x; apply lorL.
apply lorR1; apply lexistsR with x; reflexivity.
Lemma lorexistsD (f : T -> A) (P : A) {H : Inhabited T} : (Exists a, f a) \\// P -|- Exists a, (f a \\// P).
split; [apply lorexistsDL; apply H| apply lorexistsDR].
Lemma landforallDL (f : T -> A) (P : A) : (Forall a, f a) //\\ P |-- Forall a, (f a //\\ P).
apply lforallR; intro a; apply landR.
apply landL1; apply lforallL with a; reflexivity.
Lemma landforallDR {H: Inhabited T} (f : T -> A) (P : A) : Forall a, (f a //\\ P) |-- (Forall a, f a) //\\ P.
apply lforallR; intro a; apply lforallL with a; apply landL1; reflexivity.
apply lforallL with a; apply landL2; reflexivity.
Lemma landforallD (f : T -> A) (P : A) {H : Inhabited T} : (Forall a, f a) //\\ P -|- Forall a, (f a //\\ P).
Lemma lorforallDL (f : T -> A) (P : A) : (Forall a, f a) \\// P |-- Forall a, (f a \\// P).
apply lforallR; intro a; apply lorL.
apply lforallL with a; apply lorR1; reflexivity.
Lemma limplTrue P : ltrue -->> P -|- P.
apply limplL; [apply ltrueR| apply landL1; reflexivity].
Lemma limplexistsE (P : T -> A) (Q : A) : (Exists x, P x) -->> Q -|- Forall x, (P x -->> Q).
Lemma limplforallER (P : T -> A) (Q : A) : Exists x, (P x -->> Q) |-- (Forall x, P x) -->> Q.
Lemma lforallR2 (P : A) (Q : T -> A) (H : P |-- lforall Q) : forall x, P |-- Q x.
Lemma lexistsL2 (P : T -> A) (Q : A) (H : lexists P |-- Q) : forall x, P x |-- Q.
Lemma landtrueL : forall a, ltrue //\\ a -|- a.
Lemma landtrueR : forall a, a //\\ ltrue -|- a.
Lemma curry : forall a b c, (a //\\ b) -->> c -|- a -->> (b -->> c).

Global Instance ILogicOps_Prop : ILogicOps Prop := {| lentails P Q := (P : Prop) -> Q; ltrue := True; lfalse := False; limpl P Q := P -> Q; land P Q := P /\ Q; lor P Q := P \/ Q; lforall T F := forall x:T, F x; lexists T F := exists x:T, F x |}.

command: intros P Q R [HPQ HQP] [HQR HRQ]; split; etransitivity; eassumption.
apply lforallR; intro x; destruct x.
apply lexistsL; intro x; destruct x.
apply lforallR; intro x; apply lforallL with x.
intros P P' HP; split; apply lforall_lentails_m; intro x; apply HP.
apply lexistsL; intro x; apply lexistsR with x.
intros P P' HP; split; apply lexists_lentails_m; intro x; apply HP.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ; split; intros H.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ.
apply landR; [apply landL1 | apply landL2]; assumption.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ.
split; apply land_lentails_m; (apply HP || apply HQ).
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ.
apply lorL; [apply lorR1 | apply lorR2]; assumption.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ.
split; apply lor_lentails_m; (apply HP || apply HQ).
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ; red in HP.
apply limplAdj; rewrite <- HQ, HP; apply landAdj; reflexivity.
intros P P' HP Q Q' HQ.
split; apply limpl_lentails_m; (apply HP || apply HQ).
intros HQR P G HPQ HG.
split; apply lorL; [apply lorR2 | apply lorR1 | apply lorR2 | apply lorR1]; reflexivity.
split; apply lorL; try apply lorL; [ apply lorR1 | apply lorR2; apply lorR1 | apply lorR2; apply lorR2 | apply lorR1; apply lorR1 | apply lorR1; apply lorR2 | apply lorR2 ]; reflexivity.
apply landR; [apply landAdj | apply landL2]; reflexivity.
apply landAdj; apply lexistsL; intro a; apply limplAdj; apply lexistsR with a; reflexivity.
apply lexistsL; intro a; apply landR.
apply landL1; apply lexistsR with a; reflexivity.
apply lexistsL; intro x; apply lexistsR with x; apply lorR1; reflexivity.
destruct H as [[x]]; apply lexistsR with x; apply lorR2; reflexivity.
apply lexistsL; intro x; apply lorL.
apply lorR1; apply lexistsR with x; reflexivity.
split; [apply lorexistsDL; apply H| apply lorexistsDR].
apply lforallR; intro a; apply landR.
apply landL1; apply lforallL with a; reflexivity.
apply lforallR; intro a; apply lforallL with a; apply landL1; reflexivity.
apply lforallL with a; apply landL2; reflexivity.
apply lforallR; intro a; apply lorL.
apply lforallL with a; apply lorR1; reflexivity.
apply limplL; [apply ltrueR| apply landL1; reflexivity].
